valueToArrayList

public static ArrayList<String> valueToArrayList(byte[] buffer,
                                                 int dataType,
                                                 int numElems)
Transform a set of values into a string representation. A binary array of bytes are parsed based on the given data type. The value of each element, up to the number of elements given, is transformed.

Parameters:
buffer - the bytes containing the value.

Returns:
